male, 4.6 mm (OMNH-Ar-11277) and ovigerous female, 7.4 mm (OMNH-Ar-11278), Shirahama , Iriomote Island , Okinawa Prefecture , 24°21'44"N , 123°44'45"E (
), 0.05 m depth
, dead coral and fine sand bottom, 16 July 2015 , coll. H. Ariyama ;
